This scrip download the source from git
The generated package will be installed in /opt so that is can exist side another wine in /usr

These are not addressed for now, to integrate with desktop
symbolic link to wine64 and wine from home should work
/usr/share/applications/
/usr/bin/

Installing multilib for Slackware 15 is enough to build

This is experimental and incomplete
default kernel and generic configuration is not recommended
to get the most performance out of this

dependencies for Arch installation for comparison
